          "2 – Jamāʿa b. Saʿd,  al-Juʿfī.  al-Ṣā’igh (the jeweler).  Narrated from Abū ʿAbdillāh   . عليه السلام Went out with Abū al-Khaṭṭāb and was killed.  He is weak in his ḥadīth.  His madhhab is what I have mentioned."
